MINDBLOCK: Block psionic attacks

Syntax: mindblock
        psi mind block

DESCRIPTION:
  Raise a psionic shield that blocks psionic attacks for about ten minutes.
  Costs 4 ISP. Affects self only.

NOTES:
  You must know mind block and have enough ISP.
  In combat, using psionics costs one attack from your APM pool.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics
